For the person who hesitates to burn a candle, we have the answer! The bulb in our Candle Warmer melts the candle, in just a few hours, as it sits in our unique metal rack giving a scent without any open flame. Use our candle warmer refills or melt regular jar candles up to 4 3/4" wide or oval candles that do not fit in ceramic warmers. Plus you get the added benefit of a lovely nightlight on nearby walls! 1 candelabra socket, 60 watts maximum; Bulb included. Always use a straight sided jar candle for warming, not included. Made in the USA.

Our Medium Wellington Light is a stately commanding light that
 will grace any living area of your home. Chosen most often for in the

well for in the game room or over a table. Featuring heavy wood 
crossbar with wrought iron scroll brackets, the Medium Wellington Hanging
 Light is accented with Kettle Black shades. Includes canopy kit,  7-feet of cord and 3-feet of chain for hardwire installation. Standard sockets, 2 x 60 watts maximum wattage. UL listed for dry locations. Made in the USA.

The Round Tapered Pan Candle Holder in Antique Tin has a large pan for displaying bowl fillers or small collections of shells, cones, beads or potpourri. Antique tin finish. Solid metal construction. Holds a regular or battery operated taper which is not included.

The Candle Stand in Antique Tin is a country farmhouse decorator's dream. The Candle Stand resembles an upside down funnel with a candle holder on top. Antique tin finish. Solid metal construction. Holds a regular or battery operated taper which is not included.

Our wrought iron courting candle is reminiscent of those that adorned many Amish and Mennonite homes of our region in past generations. The father of the young would set the height of the candle so her suitor would know when it was time to be heading home. Smokey black finish. Solid metal construction. Holds a regular or battery operated taper which is not included.

A wonderful reproduction of an antique lantern from Irvin's collection. Our Primitive Candle Lantern has a hook for hanging from the ceiling or a wall hook. Rustic Tin finish. Handcrafted in Pennsylvania. Rustic Tin Finish. Made in the USA. .

Our adorable Angel Candle Holder will be a piece to pass down through the generations. This well made metal angel is a sturdy yet stunning addition to your holiday decor. Smokey black finish. Solid metal construction. Holds a regular or battery operated taper which is not included.

Double wreath hook. Decorate by putting a wreath on both sides of your door. Country Tin finish. Handcrafted in Pennsylvania. Country Tin Finish. Use to hang a wreath on one or both sides of the door. Made in the USA.

Our impressive Long Match Holder in Antique Tin is the perfect holder for long fireplace matches. Anyone with a working fireplace will appreciate a beautiful holder to accompany the long matchsticks. Antique tin finish. Solid metal construction. .

Our original matchbox has been brought back to grace our line with utilitarian charm. The Match Box in Antique Tin is a former staple for every home. Antique tin finish. Solid metal construction. Matches not included.

The unique look of our reproduction Comb Box in Enameled Whtie is reminiscent of a years gone by home staple. In the earlier years of the 1900's every home had a comb box of some type. White finish with black accent. Solid metal construction. Has glass mirror.
A great decorative piece to sit on a kitchen shelf or on your window sill. Place a tealight underneath the great for a warm welcoming glow. Imported. Smokey black finish. . .

A punched metal bowl/tray that could be used a variety of ways in your home. Fill it with rag ball like we have done or add a cloth napkin and use it for seasonal items to enhance your home. Imported. Smokey black finish. . .

Our Teapot with tinpunch design will make a great silk floral arrangement base as well as a decorative accent in the primitive kitchen. Smokey Black finish. Lid opens to hold decorative flowers or other items. Imported. . .

A beautiful way to disguise your needed paper towels on the kitchen counter. Our Punched Tin Paper Towel Dispenser is a beautifully appointed statement of farmhouse simplicity. Antique tin finish. Solid punched tin construction. Remove top to insert paper towel roll.

A beautiful way to disguise your needed paper towels on the kitchen counter. Our Punched Tin Paper Towel Dispenser is a beautifully appointed statement of farmhouse simplicity. Smokey black finish. Solid punched tin construction. Remove top to insert paper towel roll.

A reproduction of a long time favorite Irvin's piece, our Heart Cheese Mold will be just the right addition to your shelf or table. Imagine it lying on it's side with a small battery pillar candle nestled inside. Or in it's normal position filled with a large battery pillar and potpourri. Textured black finish. Not food safe, decorative only. Made in the USA.

The Oval Tray in White Enamel is a great piece to contain clutter in the bathroom, powder room or kitchen counter. The easy clean enameled finish makes this a perfect choice. Imported. White finish with black accent. Solid metal construction. .

The 3 Tier Wire Organizer in Smokey Black is the standard in farmhouse decorating today. Imagine how beautifully organized your counter will be with everything in it's place and a place for everything! Imported. Smokey black finish. Solid metal construction. Metal handle with wooden bale.

Irvin's has brought back a piece from his early days of tinsmithing. The Decorative Mug in Antique Tin is a reproduction of an original that Irvin had actually reproduced in the early 80's. This piece goes well with farmhouse and colonial decors. Not for use with food.  Imported. Antique tin finish. Solid metal construction. .

Irvin's has brought back a piece from his early days of tinsmithing. The Decorative Mug in White is a reproduction of an original that Irvin had actually reproduced in the early 80's. This piece goes well with farmhouse and country decors. White finish. Solid metal construction. .

The Bread Box in Antique Tin is a grand piece that will complete farmhouse charm to your kitchen or pantry counter.  This anchor piece has one large interior cavity to keep all of your bread and rolls. Imported. Antique tin finish. .

The Salt and Pepper Shaker Holder in Antique Tin is a fabulous piece to use in your country or farmhouse kitchen. Each holder comes with mason jar shakers with a nickel finished top. A wonderful housewarming or shower gift for friends and family! Imported. Antique tin finish. Glass shakers included. Solid metal construction.

The reintroduction of an extremely popular piece from the early days of Irvin's Country Tinware, our Napkin and Shaker Holder will include two beautiful mason jar shakers with nickel finished tops. Antique tin finish. Glass shakers included. Solid metal construction.

column4: Rustic beauty meets a pinch of garden-inspired magic in this beautiful lantern, suitable for table placement or hanging in your home, porch, or patio. Sturdy mango wood forms the elegant curves of this conservatory-inspired design, finished with a rustic natural stain that elevates its natural appeal. The open sides allow you to let your creative imagination run free - ideal for pairing with tablescapes in a cottage-aesthetic wedding or outdoor event. This lovely lantern is right at home in a variety of decorating styles, from the glass cylinder in the center to the ring-style hanging finial perched at the top. Crafted from solid mango tree wood with a faux-aged metal hanging ring at the peak.. This lantern will come empty with the glass cylinder in the center, ready for your customization; candle and greenery shown in product photos are for illustrative purposes only..

Paul Revere lamp is a staple in country living and rustic farmhouse decor. This weathered grey zinc base is decorated with layers of stamped metal that shine like geometric starbursts. Use the three-way switch to control the shaded bulb on top and cast a warm glow through base.  The 15-Inch Gray Check fabric shade is included. Weathered Zinc finish. 3-way switch; E26/Medium (Standard) socket in top, 1 x 60 watts maximum watts; E12/Candelabra socket in bottom, 1 x 25 watts. Has a 6-foot cord; Includes 7-Inch harp and finial. Shade included.

The nostalgic silhouette of a farmhouse perched on rolling hills meets a country aesthetic in this charming table lamp. The base is formed of a simple metal saltbox farmhouse, complete with four tiny windows on each side. Just above the roof, a classic 15-Inch gray check lampshade offers a soft glow to your favorite room or corner, gently shining down on the little house below. An ideal addition to your country decor, cottage themed room, or favorite reading nook. This farmhouse-inspired design is both imaginative and welcoming, and a great way to make guests feel instantly at home. Weathered Zinc finish. 1 E26/Medium (Standard) socket, 60 watts maximum. Has a 6-foot cord; Includes 7-Inch harp and finial. Shade included.

A beautiful open bottom lamp with a traditional folk art willow tree shade. Has a 7-foot cord and 3-way switch; Plugs into wall outlet; E26/Medium (Standard) socket in top, 1 x 150 watts maximum watts; E12/Candelabra socket in bottom, 1 x 60 watts. Shade included. Shade included. Smokey black finish.

Take a step through time and peer into the romance of the past with this antiqued lamp crafted in the colonial style. This table lamp is wrought with a smokey black finish to give it an authentic rustic feel. Solid metal caging around the base encases a secondary bulb, giving it the silhouette of a real antique lantern. A latched front allows you to change out the bulb of the electric 'candle' inside, or add in greenery, flowers, or other small decorative accents. Both bulbs are independently operated and may also be used in tandem when extra illumination is needed. Brighten up the room with both bulbs or keep the night cozy and intimate by using the glow of the smaller interior light. With an all metal antique-finished design, this handsome lantern-style lamp adds an appealing historical element to your home's decor. Smokey Black finish. 3-way switch; E26/Medium (Standard) socket in top, 1 x 150 watts maximum watts; E12/Candelabra socket in bottom, 1 x 25 watts. Has a 6-foot cord; Includes 7-Inch harp and finial.
